00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,280
[Mud]
near the Second People's Hospital.

338
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,300
[Same Mud]
near the Second People's Hospital.

339
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:46,960
[Same Mud]

340
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,180
That, I can guess.

341
