[CUSTOMS INSPECTION]

391
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:21,720
[CHINA CUSTOMS]

392
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:22,500
Listen up.

393
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:23,900
From today on,

394
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:25,020
our Passenger Inspection Section I

395
00:15:25,040 --> 00:15:26,660
