414
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:02,780
Fan,

415
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:03,900
you take

416
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:04,500
Jiang Shihuo.

417
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,380
Mr. Sun,

418
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,860
please take Zhang Dayu.

419
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:19,100
Zhang Dayu, listen up.

420
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,340
Mr. Sun

421
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,660
- is our Customs - Got it.

422
00:16:21,680 --> 00:16:23,380
image champion.

423
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:24,980
Learn from him, got it?

424
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:25,740
Yes!

