488
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,580
under Chen Sanhe.

489
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:44,860
Oh right,

490
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,980
Chen Sanhe,

491
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:48,180
