498
00:19:59,080 --> 00:20:00,020
It's pretty safe.

499
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,060
So don't worry.

500
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:03,740
Well,

501
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:05,740
