502
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:07,940
Seven years in the blink of an eye.

503
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:09,940
The kid's grown up now

504
00:20:10,280 --> 00:20:11,380
and has got his own mind.

505
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:12,820
Even though

506
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:15,460
