507
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:17,540
As long as he's happy,

508
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:18,740
that's all that matters.

509
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:21,460
I've taken good care of him.

510
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,020
He's safe and sound.

511
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:24,460
So don't worry.

512
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:31,380
Special passenger.

513
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:34,420
Departure point.

514
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:35,620
Transit countries.

515
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,540
Special passenger baggage.

516
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:38,660
Transit countries.

517
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,460
Strange looks.

518
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,500
Suspicious behavior.

519
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:45,900
Mumbling what?

520
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,940
I'm memorizing the VIP passenger list.

521
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:49,860
Already on paper, no?

522
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,140
Lock it in

523
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,380
