524
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:54,740
Aren't you usually pretty confident?

525
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:55,820
What's wrong today?

526
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,180
Mr. Chen…

527
00:20:58,960 --> 00:20:59,740
it's just

528
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:00,460
I…

529
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,260
Speak your mind.

530
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:03,540
