533
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:08,060
Trying to prove yourself?

534
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:08,620
Yeah.

535
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:10,780
Then you've got
to understand yourself first.

536
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:11,980
Play to your strengths,

537
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:13,380
