539
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:15,740
I…

540
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,260
My strengths…

541
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:18,620
I know.

542
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:20,460
I'm not as good as Guo Cong,

543
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,140
or as calm as Jiang Shihuo.

544
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,580
Your biggest strength

545
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:26,380
is adaptability.

546
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:27,780
You're sharp,

547
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,540
and you've got

548
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:30,460
