568
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:13,020
Hearing you say that,

569
00:22:13,760 --> 00:22:15,180
I'm almost impressed with myself.

570
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:19,420
Remember that no-shame face of yours.

571
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,340
I'm just making

572
00:22:22,360 --> 00:22:24,020
