574
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:26,700
Make it or break it.

575
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,180
This way.

576
00:22:28,560 --> 00:22:30,180
It's on you in the moment.

577
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,620
Yes, Mr. Chen,

578
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,140
