579
00:22:33,280 --> 00:22:33,980
Take my place.

580
00:22:38,320 --> 00:22:38,740
Dayu.

581
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:40,900
Talk less,

582
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:42,380
