What did my mentor say to you?

585
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:00,860
Your mentor's impressive!

586
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:01,820
Awesome!

587
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:05,220
Stay alert, both of you.

588
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:06,980
If anything unexpected

589
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,060
