590
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:09,260
coordinate with each other.

591
00:23:09,280 --> 00:23:10,820
If needed, ask senior officers.

592
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:11,500
Yes.

593
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:12,020
Yes.

594
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:14,980
Cong, heading over there.

595
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:16,580
Hello.

596
00:23:17,120 --> 00:23:17,540
This way.

597
00:23:19,360 --> 00:23:22,840
[CHINA CUSTOMS]

598
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:30,220
Hello.

599
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:31,060
China Customs.

600
00:23:31,840 --> 00:23:32,460
Excuse me,

601
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,820
who is using this wheelchair?

602
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:34,780
I am.

603
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:35,740
Sir,

604
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:37,460
it needs to go through inspection.

605
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,420
It's just a wheelchair.

606
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:41,180
Is that really necessary?

607
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:42,380
And,

608
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:43,700
the wheelchair's loaded.

609
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:44,620
You gonna carry it

610
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,300
on and off?

611
00:23:45,320 --> 00:23:46,740
Please cooperate with us.

612
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:47,340
Your wheelchair

613
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:48,260
must be inspected.

614
00:23:48,360 --> 00:23:49,700
Why are you following me around?

615
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:50,580
No photos.

616
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:52,060
I've worked abroad for years,

617
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:53,740
been through customs tons of times,

618
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:55,020
and never once got inspected!

619
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:55,740
Step aside!

620
00:23:55,760 --> 00:23:57,020
I'm repeating this once more,

621
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,620
please cooperate
with Customs procedures.

622
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:00,380
Your wheelchair
must go through inspection.

623
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:00,860
For real?

624
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:01,540
Speed through.

625
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:02,660
If you refuse inspection,

626
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,580
you're not getting through.

627
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:04,740
Why won't you let me through?

628
00:24:04,760 --> 00:24:05,620
Because I'm with the Customs!

629
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,340
I've done nothing wrong,

630
00:24:06,360 --> 00:24:07,220
so why stop me?

631
00:24:07,240 --> 00:24:08,060
I'm doing my job.

632
00:24:08,280 --> 00:24:08,740
You…

633
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:10,260
What's this attitude?

634
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:11,100
Calm down, sir.

635
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:11,500
Relax,

636
00:24:11,520 --> 00:24:12,420
we'll handle it

637
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:13,220
properly.

638
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:13,940
Move along.

639
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:14,780
What's going on?

640
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:16,940
He refused inspection.

641
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:17,620
Something's off.

642
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,460
What's wrong with me?

643
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:20,380
Listen up,

644
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,260
quit your nonsense!

645
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,340
Sir.

646
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,500
Can we look into the situation first?

647
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:25,660
Cong,

648
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:26,500
you sure he's dirty?

649
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,420
I'm sure.

650
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,180
I'm not mistaken!

651
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:29,900
I'm telling you,

652
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:30,660
don't hold me up!

653
00:24:30,680 --> 00:24:31,580
Calm down, please.

654
00:24:31,600 --> 00:24:32,180
Deng,

655
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,260
we've got a situation.

656
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,180
Please come

657
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:34,940
to the diversion lane.

658
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:35,820
Copy that.

659
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:36,340
A sec.

660
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:37,380
Why are you stopping me?

661
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:37,940
Yeah.

662
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:38,820
I did nothing wrong!

663
00:24:38,840 --> 00:24:40,060
Please wait a moment.

664
00:24:40,080 --> 00:24:41,060
- Hello, sir. - Please don't shout.

665
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:41,780
That's ridiculous!

666
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:42,700
Why can't I go through?

667
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,500
This is our senior.

668
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:45,060
- Easy now, don't worry. - Don't worry.

669
00:24:45,080 --> 00:24:46,300
My colleague

670
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:47,060
was out of line.

671
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:47,860
I apologize

672
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:48,940
on his behalf.

673
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:50,220
Let's step aside

674
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,100
and not block

675
00:24:51,120 --> 00:24:52,740
other passengers,

676
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:53,420
okay?

677
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:54,820
That's more like it.

678
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:57,980
I'm not unreasonable.

679
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,580
We can talk!

680
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:00,300
Yes.

681
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:01,100
Unlike him,

682
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:03,220
he came at me like a roadblock,

683
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:04,220
glaring at me.

684
00:25:04,240 --> 00:25:05,060
No way I'm taking that!

685
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,860
You refused to cooperate first, okay?

686
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:07,820
You… see?

687
00:25:07,840 --> 00:25:08,380
Guo Cong.

688
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:09,980
Look at him!

689
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:11,020
Here's the thing,

690
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,780
in our work,

691
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:14,460
we do have the authority

692
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:16,540
to require baggage inspection.

693
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,380
We hope for your understanding.

694
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:19,060
Well,

695
00:25:19,160 --> 00:25:21,140
we'll have a colleague
help move your wheelchair.

696
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:21,700
Is that okay?

697
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,300
Stop filming.

698
00:25:22,320 --> 00:25:23,020
No photos, please.

699
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:23,700
Alright, fine.

700
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:25,260
Scan it then.

701
00:25:26,120 --> 00:25:26,980
Thanks.

702
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:27,740
Guo Cong,

703
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,460
go ahead.

704
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:29,740
Cong.

705
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:32,220
Sir,

706
00:25:32,800 --> 00:25:33,820
please don't film.

707
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:35,700
Appreciate it.

708
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,260
Please step aside.

709
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:38,980
Thank you.

710
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:39,980
Speed through.

711
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:40,780
Thank you.

712
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:42,020
Sir, let me…

713
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,100
How ridiculous!

714
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:44,900
Deng, thanks.

715
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:55,980
No issues.

716
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:56,500
Calm down.

717
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:57,420
Easy now.

718
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:58,980
We're not targeting you on purpose.

719
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,460
Then why was I stopped?

720
00:26:00,840 --> 00:26:01,340
Well…

721
00:26:01,360 --> 00:26:02,180
Where's your boss?

722
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,180
Who's in charge?

723
00:26:03,760 --> 00:26:04,300
Sir.

724
00:26:04,320 --> 00:26:04,820
Easy now.

725
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:05,420
Just breathe.

726
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,420
I'm not talking to you.

727
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,780
You're not at fault.

728
00:26:08,520 --> 00:26:09,620
But your colleague,

729
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,100
I will be filing a complaint.

730
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:12,540
What's that attitude?

731
00:26:12,560 --> 00:26:13,020
Calm down,

732
00:26:13,040 --> 00:26:13,540
please.

733
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,660
Complaint number?

734
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:17,060
12360.

735
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:21,260
This is outrageous!

736
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:24,420
What bad luck!

737
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:28,060
Cong,

738
00:26:28,280 --> 00:26:29,140
don't sweat it.

739
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,540
Anyone can misjudge.

740
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:32,620
We'll avoid it next time, right?

741
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:35,380
Thanks

742
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:36,100
for helping me out.

743
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:38,220
Don't mention it!

744
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:41,380
Hello.

745
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:47,000
[CHINA CUSTOMS]

746
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:58,460
I just stepped away for a moment,

747
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:01,020
and you two already
got a complaint filed.

748
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,580
Nice work!

749
00:27:05,040 --> 00:27:05,860
Guo Cong,

750
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,220
wanna hear

751
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:08,500
how the passenger

752
00:27:08,520 --> 00:27:09,620
described you?

753
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:11,860
He called you a bandit!

754
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:12,820
A roadblock!

755
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:17,980
Weren't you usually calm?

756
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:19,620
What happened once you were on duty?

757
00:27:26,840 --> 00:27:27,700
Heads up!

758
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,420
Own your mistakes.

759
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:32,620
Take your hits at attention!

760
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:35,740
Acting wronged,

761
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,700
who's that for?

762
00:27:41,280 --> 00:27:41,700
Now,

763
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,420
tell me,

764
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:46,620
how did you misjudge the case?

765
00:27:49,840 --> 00:27:51,500
He came back from Kenya alone,

766
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:52,860
with an old wheelchair.

767
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:54,540
I thought

768
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:55,700
he fit

769
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:57,580
the high-risk ivory smuggler profile

770
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,620
in the Risk Assessment Guidelines…

771
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:01,900
The guidelines are dead, you're not!

772
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:03,100
You've learned nothing?

773
00:28:03,120 --> 00:28:03,660
No.

774
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,780
Aren't you usually smart?

775
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:07,780
What went wrong this time?

776
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:08,860
You misjudged

777
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,340
and started throwing attitude!

778
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:11,420
What were you thinking?

779
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,780
This uniform

780
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:15,140
is to give you discipline,

781
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,740
not attitude!

782
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:21,860
And you!

783
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,380
How did you handle the situation?

784
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:26,900
Mentor.

785
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:28,300
Did I tell you to speak?

786
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,900
Now you wanna act like brothers?

787
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:33,060
Too late!

788
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,020
Come,

789
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:35,500
over here.

790
00:28:35,800 --> 00:28:36,500
Right here.

791
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:37,860
Show me

792
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,380
how you used your 'enthusiasm'

793
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:40,980
to calm the passenger.

794
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:41,660
Come on.

795
00:28:41,840 --> 00:28:42,380
Act!

796
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,180
Mentor.

797
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:45,700
It was Dayu who helped resolve it.

798
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,620
By the time he stepped in,

799
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:49,100
honestly, I already knew

800
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:50,220
I had misjudged it.

801
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:54,380
The man was wearing

802
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:56,140
outdated clothes,

803
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,380
clearly worn at the collar.

804
00:28:58,800 --> 00:28:59,980
He's frugal.

805
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:02,020
There was medicated plaster

806
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:02,900
on the side of his bag.

807
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,020
He'd shake

808
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,260
his right leg to ease it

809
00:29:05,280 --> 00:29:05,860
after long standing.

810
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:06,580
So his right leg

811
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:07,980
must've been injured before.

812
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:10,460
He probably bought
that wheelchair back then.

813
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,340
He brought it

814
00:29:12,600 --> 00:29:13,260
back home

815
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:14,620
because he didn't wanna waste it.

816
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,700
So he works abroad

817
00:29:16,080 --> 00:29:17,220
in Africa.

818
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:19,260
You've got it all figured out now.

819
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:23,100
So why did you
block him at the checkpoint?

820
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:25,380
Things got tense just now.

821
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,780
Lots of people were filming.

822
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:27,980
If I just let him go,

823
00:29:28,040 --> 00:29:28,580
I was afraid…

824
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,260
Afraid what?

825
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:32,020
It would make you lose face, right?

826
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:33,460
It would

827
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,420
damage the Customs image.

828
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,260
Oh, thanks a lot!

829
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:37,900
You've completely

830
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,180
embarrassed Customs!

831
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:48,380
Get out!

832
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:53,820
Making a misjudgment isn't shameful.

833
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:55,540
But being overly cautious is!

834
00:29:58,080 --> 00:29:59,580
Have you ever thought about

835
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,460
how these returning citizens

836
00:30:01,520 --> 00:30:02,660
truly feel?

837
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:04,060
What is going through their minds?

838
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:07,300
Have you ever
thought about what your uniforms mean,

839
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:08,660
and what your duty is?

840
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:10,020
On your very first day

841
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,020
when you joined Customs,

842
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,220
I told you,

843
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:14,500
Customs is the country's calling card!

844
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:15,980
When you stand there,

845
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,100
you're not just yourselves.

846
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:19,340
You represent the country.

847
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,660
Be approachable, but hold the line.

848
00:30:21,680 --> 00:30:22,620
Six simple words.

849
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:23,580
Easy to say.

850
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:24,860
Hard to live by.

851
00:30:34,280 --> 00:30:35,220
Don't just stand there,

852
00:30:36,280 --> 00:30:37,780
go back and think it through!

853
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:39,260
Write

854
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:40,660
a 1,000-word reflection

855
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:41,540
and hand it in tomorrow!

856
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:42,220
Yes.

857
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:42,900
Yes.

858
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:50,820
Is the job

859
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:51,580
not going smoothly?

860
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:55,620
You've only just started.

861
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:56,340
Don't rush.

862
00:30:57,840 --> 00:30:59,180
It's like fishing.

863
00:30:59,560 --> 00:31:01,220
Who gets a bite

864
00:31:01,240 --> 00:31:02,420
right after casting the bait?

865
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:03,700
You've got to wait.

866
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,260
You need patience.

867
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:07,580
Good news takes time.

868
00:31:08,600 --> 00:31:10,780
You expect a beginner not to be antsy?

869
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:13,580
When there's no bite for ages,

870
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,580
you can't resist yanking it up.

871
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,820
So did you yank it up,

872
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,620
or

873
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:21,660
scare the fish off?

874
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:25,940
I wrote a reflection.

875
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:30,940
I figured

876
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,460
you were just a bit impulsive,

877
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:33,540
made a small mistake.

878
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:34,940
But a reflection?

879
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,980
You're really surprising me!

880
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,580
Uncle, can you stop teasing me?

881
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,380
Alright,

882
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:44,500
I'm not

883
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,380
teasing you.

884
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,220
So tell me,

885
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,580
what mistake did you make?

886
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,020
We have rules.

887
00:31:53,360 --> 00:31:55,060
What happens in Customs
stays in Customs.

888
00:31:56,760 --> 00:31:57,660
It's fine.

889
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:00,100
Just a little hardship.

890
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:01,020
I'll chew it over

891
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:01,860
and swallow it.

