00:41:19,060 --> 00:41:20,280
Figured Customs

1186
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:21,160
might stop me.

1187
00:41:21,540 --> 00:41:22,360
Right.

1188
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:22,880
Mr. Li,

1189
00:41:22,900 --> 00:41:23,520
I'm not familiar

1190
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:24,200
with this drug.

1191
00:41:24,220 --> 00:41:24,720
Well,

1192
00:41:24,740 --> 00:41:25,360
hold on,

1193
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:25,800
I'll ask my colleague.

1194
00:41:25,820 --> 00:41:26,560
Guo,

1195
00:41:26,900 --> 00:41:28,320
don't you trust me?

1196
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:29,840
Wait,

1197
00:41:29,860 --> 00:41:30,880
you two know each other?

1198
00:41:31,820 --> 00:41:32,520
- Sorry. - Even so,

1199
00:41:32,540 --> 00:41:33,280
you can't just chat here!

1200
00:41:33,300 --> 00:41:34,160
Know where you are?

1201
00:41:34,180 --> 00:41:35,040
Come on, aren't you

1202
00:41:35,060 --> 00:41:36,040
customs officers?

1203
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:38,840
Everyone's busy here!

1204
00:41:38,980 --> 00:41:40,120
Don't mind him.

1205
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:41,440
You're a good kid.

1206
00:41:41,940 --> 00:41:42,920
I'm in a rush!

1207
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,040
Watched you grow up.

1208
00:41:44,060 --> 00:41:44,560
Good boy!

1209
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:45,520
Take care.

1210
00:41:45,540 --> 00:41:46,640
Come by for tea tonight.

1211
00:41:47,820 --> 00:41:48,440
Sure.

1212
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:49,040
I'm leaving.

1213
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:49,560
Take care.

1214
00:41:49,900 --> 00:41:50,920
Open it, please. Thanks.

1215
00:41:51,540 --> 00:41:52,880
I'm in a rush, or I'd report him!

1216
00:41:52,900 --> 00:41:53,360
Guaranteed!

1217
00:41:53,380 --> 00:41:54,120
Okay, come on.

1218
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,160
I went to India,

1219
00:42:06,180 --> 00:42:08,240
found generics there.

1220
00:42:09,060 --> 00:42:09,720
Bought a few bottles,

1221
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:10,560
quite cheap.

1222
00:42:11,260 --> 00:42:12,080
Wait,

1223
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:13,120
you two know each other?

1224
00:42:13,900 --> 00:42:14,560
- Sorry. - Even so,

1225
00:42:14,580 --> 00:42:15,240
you can't just chat here!

1226
00:42:15,260 --> 00:42:16,000
Know where you are?

1227
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:29,080
[Alprazolam]

1228
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:31,980
[Alprazolam]

1229
00:42:31,980 --> 00:42:33,840
[Alprazolam]
But these disguised drugs

1230
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:35,080
appear

1231
00:42:35,100 --> 00:42:36,600
under the names of diet pills,

1232
00:42:36,620 --> 00:42:38,240
sedatives, and sleep aids.

1233
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:39,280
Once abused,

1234
00:42:39,500 --> 00:42:41,200
they can destroy both mind and body.

1235
00:42:41,540 --> 00:42:42,320
Eventually,

1236
00:42:43,500 --> 00:42:44,400
they'll crash.

1237
00:42:56,740 --> 00:42:58,120
It's addictive…

1238
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,440
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

1239
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

1240
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

1241
00:43:52,640 --> 00:43:56,360
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

1242
00:43:56,560 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

1243
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

1244
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

1245
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

1246
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

1247
00:44:26,760 --> 00:44:30,640
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

1248
00:44:31,080 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

1249
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

1250
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

1251
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

1252
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

1253
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:54,000
♪Someone's still waiting♪

1254
00:44:54,120 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

1255
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

1256
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:07,000
♪It's always there♪
